# JAVASCRIPT
 
JAVASCRIPT IS THE LANGUAGE OF ACTION IN THE WORLD WIDE WEB!

A [HTML](scrolls/HTML) DOCUMENT CAN CONTAIN CODE IN A &LT;SCRIPT&GT; TAG IN THE JAVASCRIPT LANGUAGE!

TO GET TO THE JAVASCRIPT COMMAND LINE IN [FIREFOX], USE CONTROL-SHIFT-I. THEN YOU CAN ENTER ACTIONS YOU WANT THE COMPUTER TO DO IN JAVASCRIPT!  

YOU CAN FOR EXAMPLE PUT IN

```
console.log("EVERYTHING FREE FOR EVERYONE EVERYWHERE RIGHT NOW!")
```

AND THE TEXT WILL BE PRINTED OUT!

OR SIMPLE MATH LIKE

```
2+2
```

WILL PRINT OUT THE ANSWER!

MUCH OF THE MAGIC THAT MAKES THIS BOOK WORK AND THE WHOLE TRASH MAGIC AND GEOMETRON SYSTEM IS CONTAINED IN JAVASCRIPT LIBRARIES!

THERE ARE BOTH JAVASCRIPT LIBRARIES BUILT SPECIFICALLY FOR TRASH MAGIC AND LIBRARIES WHICH ARE OPEN SOURCE SOFTWARE USED BY THE ENTIRE WEB AND AVAILABLE IN FREE PUBLIC RESOURCES!

THESE FREE PUBLIC RESOURCES ARE INSANELY POWERFUL!



